## You must report changes
If there are changes that may affect the benefit you receive, you must notify Nav immediately. See [nav.no/rettogplikt](https://nav.no/rettogplikt).

## You have the right to appeal
You may appeal within {{klagefristUker}} weeks from the date you received the decision. You will find the form and information at [nav.no/klage](https://nav.no/klage).

